classes.name: GamsBonmin
classes.brief:
GAMS interface to Bonmin MINLP solver

Connects GAMS to COIN-OR Bonmin for mixed-integer nonlinear programming.

classes.name: GamsCbc
classes.brief:
GAMS interface to CBC MIP solver

Connects GAMS modeling environment to COIN-OR CBC.

**GamsCbc Class:**
- gmo/gev: GAMS modeling object and environment handles
- setupProblem()/setupParameters(): Configure CBC from GAMS
- Solve trace support for performance analysis

classes.name: GamsCbcHeurSolveTrace
classes.brief:
CBC heuristic for GAMS solve trace reporting

CbcHeuristic implementation that reports bound progress
to GAMS solve trace data structure for performance analysis.

classes.name: GamsCouenne
classes.brief:
GAMS interface to Couenne global optimizer

Connects GAMS to COIN-OR Couenne for global optimization of
non-convex MINLP problems via spatial branch-and-bound.

classes.name: GamsIpopt
classes.brief:
GAMS interface to Ipopt NLP solver

Connects GAMS modeling environment to COIN-OR Ipopt.

**GamsIpopt Class:**
- ipopt: SmartPtr to IpoptApplication
- nlp: GamsNLP problem representation
- Warmstart support for sequential solves

classes.name: GamsJournal
classes.brief:
Ipopt Journal implementation for GAMS output

Routes Ipopt logging through GAMS environment (gev) routines.
Supports configurable status file output levels.

classes.name: GamsMINLP
classes.brief:
Bonmin TMINLP implementation for GAMS models

GamsMINLP: Implements Bonmin::TMINLP using GMO for MINLP evaluation.
Handles variable types, SOS constraints, and branching priorities.

classes.name: GamsMessageHandler
classes.brief:
CoinMessageHandler implementation for GAMS output

Routes COIN-OR messages through GAMS environment (gev) logging.
Thread-safe via shared mutex for concurrent solver access.

classes.name: GamsNLP
classes.brief:
Ipopt TNLP implementation for GAMS models

GamsNLP: Implements Ipopt::TNLP using GMO (GAMS Modeling Object)
for objective/constraint evaluation, Jacobian sparsity, Hessian.

classes.name: GamsOsi
classes.brief:
GAMS interface to OSI-compatible solvers

Connects GAMS to commercial solvers (CPLEX, Gurobi, Mosek, Xpress)
via the COIN-OR Open Solver Interface.

classes.name: GamsOsiHelper
classes.brief:
GAMS-OSI data transfer utilities

Helper functions for loading LP problems from GMO to OSI,
storing solutions from OSI to GMO, and writing problem files.

classes.name: GamsScip
classes.brief:
GAMS interface to SCIP solver

Connects GAMS to SCIP for constraint integer programming.
Supports LP, MIP, MINLP, and general constraint optimization.

classes.name: GamsSoPlex
classes.brief:
GAMS interface to SoPlex LP solver

Connects GAMS modeling environment to the ZIB SoPlex
simplex-based LP solver.

classes.name: event_solvetrace
classes.brief: event handler to write GAMS solve trace file
